					<h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Free ASL Dictionary</h1>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f920f37 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="f920f37" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Our ASL dictionary includes over 2,300 words and phrases from our <a href="https://www.startasl.com/learn-american-sign-language">Complete 4-Level ASL Course</a>.</p>								</div>
