		<div  class="elementor-element elementor-element-813aea0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="813aea0" data-element_type="container">
				<div  class="elementor-element elementor-element-c755f8a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="c755f8a" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a name="books"></a>The Best Sign Language Dictionary Recommendations</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div  class="elementor-element elementor-element-8318497 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8318497" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Want to learn even more vocabulary? A hard copy sign language dictionary is always great to have around as you are learning American Sign Language! We know all the best ASL dictionaries that are accurate and have stood the test of time.</p><p><i>Please note that when you choose to purchase through the external links on this website (in many but not all cases) we will receive a referral commission. However, this commission does not influence the information we provide in this site. We always give honest opinions and reviews to share our findings, beliefs, and/or experiences. You can view our full disclosure on <a href="https://www.startasl.com/affiliate-disclosure">this page</a>.</i></p><p><strong><a href="https://amzn.to/4kS4hSS" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img title="asl dictionary | Start ASL" decoding="async" class="wp-image-606697 alignleft perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;205&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20205&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="sign language dictionary" width="150" height="205" data-src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2.jpg 1093w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2-751x1030.jpg 751w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2-58x80.jpg 58w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2-500x686.jpg 500w" data-sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /><noscript><img title="asl dictionary | Start ASL" decoding="async" class="wp-image-606697 alignleft" src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2.jpg" alt="sign language dictionary" width="150" height="205" srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2.jpg 1093w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2-751x1030.jpg 751w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2-58x80.jpg 58w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/asl-dictionary-2-500x686.jpg 500w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /></noscript>American Sign Language Dictionary</a></strong><br />This is a huge ASL dictionary and explains more than 5,000 signs and has over 8,000 illustrations. You definitely need to have a dictionary like this if you are learning American Sign Language! When you want to look up an obscure word, it’s most likely in here!</p><p><strong><a href="https://amzn.to/4ktLspn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Gallaudet Dictionary of American Sign Language</a><a href="https://amzn.to/4ktLspn" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img title="the gallaudet dictionary of american sign language | Start ASL" decoding="async" class="alignright wp-image-606647 perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;213&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20213&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="sign language dictionary" width="150" height="213" data-src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language.jpg 1055w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language-724x1030.jpg 724w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language-56x80.jpg 56w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language-500x711.jpg 500w" data-sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /><noscript><img title="the gallaudet dictionary of american sign language | Start ASL" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignright wp-image-606647" src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language.jpg" alt="sign language dictionary" width="150" height="213" srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language.jpg 1055w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language-724x1030.jpg 724w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language-56x80.jpg 56w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/the-gallaudet-dictionary-of-american-sign-language-500x711.jpg 500w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /></noscript></a></strong><br />This is a very popular ASL dictionary. The book includes over 3,000 signs and comes with a DVD. You are able to type in a word on the DVD and the word comes up with a video in ASL. It is great for both beginners and seasoned signers. Highly recommended!</p><p><strong><a href="https://amzn.to/3Zk3WQH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The American Sign Language Handshape Dictionary</a></strong><br />This is a great resource in that the dictionary is organized by handshape, not by word. This way, when you see a sign, you are able to look it up to learn what it means. We highly recommend this book for the ASL learner.</p><p><a href="https://amzn.to/4mP5lsw" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img title="Version 100 | Start ASL" decoding="async" class="alignleft wp-image-606237 perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;208&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20208&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt width="150" height="208" data-src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing.jpg 865w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing-742x1030.jpg 742w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing-58x80.jpg 58w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing-500x694.jpg 500w" data-sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /><noscript><img title="Version 100 | Start ASL" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft wp-image-606237" src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="208" srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing.jpg 865w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing-742x1030.jpg 742w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing-58x80.jpg 58w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/Religious-Signing-500x694.jpg 500w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /></noscript></a></p><p><strong><a href="https://amzn.to/4mP5lsw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Religious Signing: A Comprehensive Guide For All Faiths</a></strong><br />If you want to learn religious signs, or plan to interpret church services, this book is wonderful! It’s a great comprehensive guide and is easy to understand. We highly recommend it!</p><p><strong><a href="https://amzn.to/4mFWXeS" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img title="random house websters asl dictionary | Start ASL" decoding="async" class="wp-image-606698 alignright perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;150&#039;%20height=&#039;225&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20150%20225&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="sign language dictionary" width="150" height="225" data-src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary.jpg 996w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary-684x1030.jpg 684w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary-53x80.jpg 53w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary-500x753.jpg 500w" data-sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /><noscript><img title="random house websters asl dictionary | Start ASL" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-606698 alignright" src="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary.jpg" alt="sign language dictionary" width="150" height="225" srcset="https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary.jpg 996w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary-684x1030.jpg 684w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary-53x80.jpg 53w, https://www.startasl.com/wp-content/uploads/random-house-websters-asl-dictionary-500x753.jpg 500w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /></noscript>Random House Webster’s American Sign Language Dictionary</a></strong><br />This dictionary is a great resource to have. It not only illustrates vocabulary in ASL (the pictures are good, but not the best), but also idiomatic expressions. Knowing expressions like these is very important when engaging in an actual conversation with a Deaf person. We recommend this dictionary for anyone learning sign language.</p><p><strong><a href="https://amzn.to/4e9YNRD" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Random House Webster&#8217;s Concise American Sign Language Dictionary</a></strong><br />This is a wonderful concise version of the Random House Webster&#8217;s full ASL dictionary. </p><p><strong><a href="https://amzn.to/4dMuhN8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ward’s Natural Sign Language Thesaurus of Useful Signs and Synonyms</a></strong><br />A great sign language thesaurus and probably the only one available!</p>								</div>
				</div>
				</div>
